name: Enum StandardOperation
text:
Defines the standard dynamic operations. The operations GET and SET must
 be used as part of a NamespaceOperation. NamedOperation can then be further used on these
 NamespaceOperations to bind the name parameter of GET and SET operations, in which case it
 disappears from their type signature.
 NamedOperation can also be used to decorate CALL and NEW operations with a
 diagnostic name, and as such it does not affect their type signature.
codes:
public enum StandardOperation
extends Enum<StandardOperation>
implements Operation
